reviewText: This DVD is a tough workout. I got it for my son, and he can't keep up with it. It wore me out in a few minutes.
summary: Harder than it looks, even for adults.
Title: Billy Blanks - Tae Bo Kicks

reviewText: My daughter loves to exercise. She likes this DVD but still finds it quiet challenging and sweats a lot when she does it. This is the type of exercise video you can do with your child and get a real recent workout.
summary: Still a challenge for my (almost) 7 yr. old
Title: Billy Blanks - Tae Bo Kicks

reviewText: Loved it...bought an adult version as well. Our kids 2-17 all use it as well....if you are an adult starting out this is a great Taebo start.
summary: Just a great thing to do with the kids
Title: Billy Blanks - Tae Bo Kicks

reviewText: This is great for beginning exercisers. It is not hard to keep up with and my children love it.
Title: Billy Blanks - Tae Bo Kicks

reviewText: A very fun work-out video to do with kids and groun-up! It's fun, entertaining, and it sure works your booty!
Title: Billy Blanks - Tae Bo Kicks

reviewText: This DVD provides a great workout for my 4 year old daughter.  She loves the moves and she walks around doing karate kicks and punches all the time...what a joy!
Title: Billy Blanks - Tae Bo Kicks

reviewText: This is an excellent exercise DVD for children.  My boys dance and kick and enjoy their way through this.  What's not to love.
Title: Billy Blanks - Tae Bo Kicks
